        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-01-17 13:03:47.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\nA lot of these M2 JUnit tests are failing on my local machine - I believe due to ordering. Please ensure that if the tests MUST run in order for all of them to work, then add annotations in order to do so.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
