          "username": "pdragosh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-01-17 13:08:09.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nThe other explanation could be the heavy use of Thread.sleep() - which should be avoided and removed. I know that's not in this test, but it is in the m2/test.",
